You may not know it, but there are other ones, alike to thee.
Do you accept this fact as the whole truth, and as the reality before you?
- Yes
	Then go further, Disgraced One.
	- Are you sure
		I... am not sure. You must choose for yourself.
	- Are you not sure
- No
	Live inside of yourself as much as you want. The day will never change.